text: "All of My Love" is a song by Destiny. The song would have been Malta's entry in the 2020 Eurovision Song Contest in Rotterdam but the contest was cancelled because of the COVID-19 pandemic. Bernarda Brunovi, Borislav Milanov, Sebastian Arman, Dag Lundberg, and Joacim Persson all wrote the song. == References == Category:2020 songs Category:Pages with unreviewed translations Category:Articles with hAudio microformats
